OL,6,FPotential profits from illegal dumping
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland far outweigh any
OL,8,Fsanctions, an Audit Office report has
OL,9,Ffound.
OL,11,FComptroller and Auditor General
OL,12,FDorinnia Carville said financial
OL,13,Fpenalties through fines and
OL,14,Fconfiscation orders are a "fraction"
OL,15,Fof the costs of dealing with waste
OL,16,Flegally.
