OL,3,CIllegal waste penalties are "fraction"
OL,4,Cof legal disposal costs
OL,6,FHer report has concluded that current
OL,7,Fmeasures for regulating and inspecting
OL,8,Fthe waste sector are not achieving
OL,9,Fvalue for money and put at risk
OL,10,Fdelivery of the Northern Ireland
OL,11,FEnvironment Agency's (NIEA)
OL,12,Fobligations to protect the environment.
OL,14,FMs Carville said the current operation
OL,15,Fof the inspection regime "does not
OL,16,Fadequately identify or discourage
OL,17,Fcriminality".
OL,19,FResponding to the report, Environment
OL,20,FMinister Andrew Muir said tackling
OL,21,Fwaste crime was a priority.
