OL,6,FThe report said that as well as
OL,7,Fcausing damage to the environment,
OL,8,Fwaste crime is estimated to cost
OL,9,Faround #34 million annually in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland, excluding the costs
OL,11,Fstemming from rectifying environmental
OL,12,Fand social harm, evaded taxes and lost
OL,13,Flegitimate business.
OL,15,FThe report said that total potential
OL,16,Fprofits from illegal dumping far
OL,17,Foutweigh the sanctions.
