OL,6,FCourt fines imposed in relation to
OL,7,Fwaste crime since 2019 amount to
OL,8,Fapproximately #1 million but the
OL,9,Freport said it is estimated that the
OL,10,Ftotal costs of legally disposing of
OL,11,Fthe waste involved in these
OL,12,Fproceedings would have been #17
OL,13,Fmillion.
OL,15,FIn addition, the report concludes that
OL,16,Fthe NIEA's current inspection
OL,17,Farrangements are "insufficient to
OL,18,Feffectively detect and prevent waste
OL,19,Fcrime".
