OL,6,FThe report said the number of planned
OL,7,Finspection visits to high-risk sites
OL,8,Fhas significantly reduced in recent
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FIn 2017-18 there were 12 planned
OL,12,Fvisits per high-risk site per year,
OL,13,Fbut this has now fallen to six or
OL,14,Feight depending on the type of site.
OL,16,FIt said that no inspections matching
OL,17,Fwaste materials arriving and leaving
OL,18,Fsites, or verifying waste on-site,
OL,19,Fhave been conducted in the last two
OL,20,Fyears.
