OL,6,FThe report also said waste carriers
OL,7,Fare not subject to any routine
OL,8,Finspection regime, and stop and search
OL,9,Foperations targeting carriers are
OL,10,F"relatively uncommon", with only one
OL,11,Fsuch operation being conducted in 2024.
OL,13,FThe report said poor data collection
OL,14,Fand management information undermines
OL,15,Fthe NIEA's ability to regulate the
OL,16,Fwaste management industry as
OL,17,Feffectively as it could.
OL,19,FIt said it also struggles to recruit
OL,20,Fand retain specialist skills in a
OL,21,Fnumber of areas.
