OL,6,FMs Carville said: "The existing
OL,7,Fapproach to regulating waste requires
OL,8,Fsignificant improvement.
OL,10,F"The current operation of the
OL,11,Finspection regime does not adequately
OL,12,Fidentify or discourage criminality.
OL,14,F"Legal enforcement activities, even
OL,15,Fwhen successful, rarely result in
OL,16,Fpolluters remediating the damage
OL,17,Fcaused.
