OL,6,F"Furthermore, financial penalties
OL,7,Fthrough fines and confiscation orders
OL,8,Fare a fraction of the costs of dealing
OL,9,Fwith the waste legally."
OL,11,F"As a result, damage is being caused
OL,12,Fto the environment and the cost for
OL,13,Fremediation often falls to taxpayers.
OL,15,F"A review of existing arrangements and
OL,16,Finspection regimes is recommended to
OL,17,Fhelp ensure future expenditure on
OL,18,Fregulating waste delivers better value
OL,19,Ffor money and more effective
OL,20,Fenvironmental protections for Northern
OL,21,FIreland."
