OL,6,FMr Muir said the recommendations of
OL,7,Fthe report would be studied carefully.
OL,9,FHe added: "Waste crime poses a serious
OL,10,Fthreat to our environment, to public
OL,11,Fhealth and to the integrity of our
OL,12,Fwaste management systems.
OL,14,F"It also undermines law-abiding
OL,15,Foperators and damages public
OL,16,Fconfidence.
