OL,6,F"Strengthening our environmental
OL,7,Fgovernance structures is a top
OL,8,Fpriority for me and I recently took
OL,9,Freceipt of and published the interim
OL,10,Freport from the independent panel that
OL,11,FI set up to bring forward proposals
OL,12,Ffor a more robust model of
OL,13,Fenvironmental governance."
OL,15,FHe added: "Whether within existing
OL,16,Fstructures or new structures, tackling
OL,17,Fwaste crime is also a priority for me
OL,18,Fand for the NIEA and we will continue
OL,19,Fto work hard on both prevention and
OL,20,Fenforcement, with a clear focus on
OL,21,Fdelivering results.
